    So, are you ready for work?"},{"Actor":"You","Replica":"- Yap."},{"Actor":"Chan","Replica":"-
    The tasks are to kill some people. Every head is paid in full. The first victim
    is stupid fatty, that often creeps out of his business."},{"Actor":"Chan","Replica":"-
    That''s his address. You can find him here, he thinks he safe. I''ll give you
    3000$ for proofs of his death."},{"Actor":"You","Replica":"- I''ll be back soon."}],"$type":"Game.DialogSystem.Dialog"}'
