  StartDialog: '{"DialogName":"sad","SaveDialog":false,"Replics":[{"Actor":"Jackson","Replica":"-
    Ok, next targets aren''t so easy. I need you to kill some mafiosas. These bastards
    killed my brothas Chookie, Cookie and Wookiee."},{"Actor":"Jackson","Replica":"-
    Their Don''s mansion is near the center of the city. Kill the boss, maybe all
    his people too. Bring here the item from the boss."},{"Actor":"Jackson","Replica":"-
    Be careful, the boss have a special armor."},{"Actor":"You","Replica":"- It''s
    very dangerous, the task for a real ninja commando. I think you need to prepare!
    Guess you''re ready for it?"},{"Actor":null,"Replica":"- I guess, that''s easy
    peasy lemon squeezy!"}],"$type":"Game.DialogSystem.Dialog"}'
